# DivePrep Buddy — Core Rules

Read `AGENTS.md` in project root before non-trivial changes.

## Product scope

Pre-dive preparation only: context selection, checklist, buddy-check, local persistence, offline PWA.

## Forbidden without explicit approval

- Backend, auth, cloud sync, LLM features
- Dive logging, decompression, gas planning
- Safety guarantees in UI copy

## Implementation norms

- Mobile-first; large tap targets
- Checklist data in `src/content/templates/`, not hardcoded in components
- Log agent decisions in `agent-runs/` when changing UX or scope
- Research source of truth: `docs/research/`

## Safety copy

Use: prepared, reviewed, verify, remember.
Avoid: safe, guaranteed, certified, approved for diving.
